            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-902578975069c77a-f09fcd twpub-902578975069c77a-6b4cd0\"><p>International donations are gratefully accepted, but we cannot make\nany statements concerning tax treatment of donations received from\noutside the United States.  U.S. laws alone swamp our small staff.</p></div>"
